                            <li>It is suggested to take off your ornaments before any contact with soil (gardening), that with physical exertion (working out) and especially with water (swimming).</li>
                            <li>Avoid all the external contact of wear and tear resistant materials (like cleaning agents, perfume, and chlorine) with jewelry as they can destroy both stones and metals.</li>
